00:16:37.193 --> 00:16:51.177
Now faith is not tomorrow; now is like my little girl says all the time: 'Daddy, we're believing for Megan's healing, not tomorrow, not the next day, but we're believing for it now.'We're believing for the manifestation now.

00:16:51.178 --> 00:16:57.879
We're believing for Megan to talk and do all the things that we need her to do now.

00:16:57.880 --> 00:17:07.010
My little girl says that all the time to me: 'Dad, we're not praying for tomorrow; we're praying for today.'Stretch your hands out right now; just believe it.

00:17:07.011 --> 00:17:17.864
Father, right now in the name of Jesus, I come before you boldly into that throne, and I say in the name of Jesus, these people are delivered.

