We speak to those things right now. We speak to the healing: be healed and whole and well by the power of the Lord; it's in us.

00:20:38.769 --> 00:20:47.048
We have authority; we have deliverance; we have the power and authority to lay hands on the sick and they shall recover.

00:20:47.049 --> 00:20:52.663
Thank you, Jesus. Thank you, Jesus, you set us free. Thank you, Lord.

00:20:52.664 --> 00:21:03.275
We have power and authority and dominion over all sickness, over all disease, and nothing shall by any means hurt us.

00:21:03.276 --> 00:21:31.278
You're a faithful God. We worship you. Oh, how he loves you and me.

